{"tid":1520321,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鬥爭，失敗，再鬥爭，再失敗","createTime":"2019-08-30T18:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T04:54:39.000Z","uid":54303,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ece2ab4f1fa4f3674d54fd872ebbcf961404c542","tid":1520321,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T18:09:50.000Z","msg":"「鬥爭，失敗，再鬥爭，再失敗，再鬥爭，直至勝利&mdash;&mdash;這就是人民的邏輯，他們也是決不會違背這個邏輯的。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東&mdash;《丟掉幻想，準備鬥爭》1949年8月14日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日絕對唔係咩end game，我地要打到贏為止！<br />\n我地可以不停咁輸，但只要政府輸一次佢地就永遠翻唔到身！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c49b0feaff358120f74fa0b22b1840c10e77268","tid":1520321,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T18:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2QRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=8bfc97db\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2QRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=e2fcc277\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupro